Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:38.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:43.65,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... because it's summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.43,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:46.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:51.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! When it's this hot in summer, \NI want to go to the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:52.71,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:58.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... I've never been \Nto the ocean, so I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My family lived deep in the mountains, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:02.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:08.28,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice, yakisoba, ramen, \Nwatermelon-splitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Those all have to do with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.73,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.61,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.09,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go to the ocean this weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:20.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, I guess I \Ndon't mind going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.50,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... Isn't the ocean \Ndangerous because of shark attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.12,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some panic movie. It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:38.21,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! I can go to \Nthe ocean without worrying, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,But animals tend to like you, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.89,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll come to you \Nwhen you're swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:50.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:57.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Swim, swim... swim, swim, swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:09.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, if it comes to it, \Nleave me behind and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:14.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're scared of the ocean, \Ncan't you just play on the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm going to the ocean, \NI would like to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't even have a swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go buy swimsuits after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting a new one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A new swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:38.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to pick a swimsuit \Nthat works for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind is in right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.45,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can just leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.87,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick the perfect swimsuit \Nfor you, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the second-year classrooms upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I felt I was being called.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:03.47,sign_5718_50_The_Lost_Swimsui,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Swimsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time shopping with friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my first time in the swimsuit \Ndepartment, so I'm excited, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That one's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:38.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.52,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And how about this flowery one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:42.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.03,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And this chic style is nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I want to try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to disturb the other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.64,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, look at this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, there are so many, I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.90,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give all my effort to \Nhelping you choose a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.29,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Hina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.02,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, try this one next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:39.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,How many more is she going to make me try on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.07,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.61,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you, but I'm surprised \Nthat was your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd pick a more revealing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.78,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've gained a little weight lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to cover my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I really was planning to buy a bikini, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:02.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,With your proportions, \NI think you're perfectly thin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.00,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from you \Nmakes me more confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try on a bikini right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.35,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She switches gears fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This one's kind of a funny shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:26.17,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the first time \Nyou've worn one like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:29.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... or to be exact,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn anything \Nbut school swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:37.64,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Then we were right \Nto go swimsuit shopping today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No high schooler wants to go to \Nthe ocean wearing a school swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning to go in my school swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.42,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The one I used in \Nelementary school still fits,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't see the need to buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.68,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That is an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:59.31,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, I still have my swimsuit \Nfrom last year, so I—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No! You have to buy a new one, Aki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use that one! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.48,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.45,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:14.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You look so composed and beautiful \Nin a swimsuit, Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You have grown-up appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You do like simple styles, \Ndon't you, Aki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:23.20,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I figure I could wear something \Nlike this at home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Or, like, when I clean the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You use yours on normal days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.33,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.73,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I only wear a swimsuit a few times \Nin a year, so it's wasted otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if that's \Neconomical or realistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.43,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now that everyone else \Nis done picking swimsuits,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.04,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I should pick one for myself, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.34,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a cute little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.43,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.88,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.59,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.93,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure any swimsuit would look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.57,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... For you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.27,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,How about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.60,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go get my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.32,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.02,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm not a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.65,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right! If that's how it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:35.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show off how grown-up \NI can look with a sexy swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I tried to pick one,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think this is quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.55,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get another...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.11,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Th-This is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wear that, Mayu-chan! \NYou'll catch a chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:02.68,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're ready \Nfor that kind of swimsuit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.70,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.57,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,-Why bananas?\N{\c&H7C1CD2&}I wonder why you can only have up to 500 yen for your snacks on field trips...\NI hear people ask if bananas count as snacks all the time, but why does that come up? Because they're cheap and there's more than one? Does that mean that it counts as a meal since it fills you up?\N{\c&H7C6055&}-I guess it doesn't really matter, but I'm curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.62,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.31,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up getting a one-piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it won't look too childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.69,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-senpai looks worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:23.95,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Is this about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry to keep you all waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-senpai, are you... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,worried about how small you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.20,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Small?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm insecure about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:47.46,Italics Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan worries about her height, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're small enough \Nthat you need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you're about average, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm only an A-cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.11,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.53,Italics Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's what she meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to go to the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I got a really nice swimsuit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.41,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited to go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.63,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat you, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.01,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, I think I might be \Nscared of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just kidding, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited to go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... it's going to be my first time \Nat the ocean, so just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is Hina-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.29,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.93,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.81,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.89,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's practicing \Nwhat to do in case of drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.89,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I'm drowni—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,S-So this is the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.39,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean! Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We need to make sure we stretch first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.31,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There! All done stretching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.88,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, though I'm not very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a good swimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.66,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai excels at all sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she's a good swimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.60,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:32.38,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you swim in a tournament \Nas an emergency substitute and win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:43.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just happened to see a photo of it \Noutside the swim team's club room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yua-chan, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.18,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I can swim fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,but if I get caught in a current, \Nmy feet won't touch the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't that mean you can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! Let's just go swim now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.71,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.33,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:18.90,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:33.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Got—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.83,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go buy some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:44.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.59,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:53.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Kuu-chan is always \Ntreating me like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the shortest in the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:59.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm still a year older than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:01.69,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,She should rely on me more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:15.24,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? I need to \Ncontact Aki-chan somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.29,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I left my cell phone back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.42,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,That little girl is out here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.35,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is she lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.25,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But she doesn't look like \Nan ordinary little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Kuroyanagi-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.48,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:43.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sensei, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.48,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filming a drama near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:49.67,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for my next scene now, \Nso I took a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.12,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you appearing in the drama, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.75,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I thought you had \Nentered show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:05.71,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was a \Nterrible shame for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.76,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,as sweet and beautiful as you \Nnot to strive for a job in show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.29,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. Since fate somehow \Nbrought us together here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.61,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you take this opportunity \Nto enter show business?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.37,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.40,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.27,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,are the girls you're usually with \Nnot here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:32.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Actually, they are here, \Nbut I've lost sight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.03,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.29,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:38.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.37,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.92,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to contact \NChiaki-san, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan sure is taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.87,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try calling her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.63,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,The line's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.73,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:12.32,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, \Nwhich direction did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.32,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think it was that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.72,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.13,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan isn't answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Should we have them make \Na lost child announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That might embarrass Mayu-senpai so much\N that she wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.22,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.86,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.00,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan left her phone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:42.07,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do we do?! \NWe have no way to contact her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She really is lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:47.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.10,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.50,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan left her phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.70,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're about to have a \Nsecond lost child on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.87,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked so much, \Nand still can't find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:25.18,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me? Oh, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:25.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she got scouted by someone in \Nshow business who happened to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and they took her to the \Nscene of a drama filming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,As cute as she is, I can believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.53,Main Dialogue,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.03,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take a picture of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah.... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.77,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're all coming to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.17,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.22,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the shore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.74,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.56,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, look! It's Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.40,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can get back to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.93,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:13.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.45,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:32.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.55,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.94,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell which of them was actually lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan and Hina-chan still aren't back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.19,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.93,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-senpai's with her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You ran into Mayu-chan while taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.20,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.13,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried, since you \Nleft your cell phones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you made it back \Nwithout losing your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:15.80,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The crabs showed me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:22.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I like mountain animals, too, \Nbut marine animals are really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:28.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Some people talked to me \Nand I turned into a scarecrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:32.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,but then Mayu-chan happened \Nto walk by and saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:35.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mayu-senpai, you weren't lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.95,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool that you helped \NHina-chan when she was in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.18,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:46.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an older sister \Nwe can all count on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.55,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,An older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.46,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.35,Main Dialogue Top,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.81,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,We won't tell anyone that \Nshe really was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.05,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.05,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.73,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The horizon looks so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.17,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And the sea breeze feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.49,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun playing with everyone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, how was your \Nfirst visit to the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could live here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:33.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you animals from the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was just a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I love all of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.97,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB8255A&}-New students welcoming party\N{\c&H7C6055&}-Welcoming party at the karaoke place near school\N-Dinner near the karaoke place\N-Planning to finish at 19:30\N-Get RSVPs and make reservations\N
