Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's all take a picture together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:01.10,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:18.92,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.88,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel sleepy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:44.91,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can all come to \Nthe ocean together again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:35.89,sign_33685_365_Trying_Too_Hard,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}Trying Too Hard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,My first visit to the ocean was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:32.33,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just play around all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:34.63,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help Kuu-chan \Nand Mayu-chan at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:36.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,and I have to study theater, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.03,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Trying Too Hard."
